subSubSection.paragraph:
Abbreviations. Sclerites:
sgp
= subgenital plate; 
svs
= subvulvar sclerite; 
vs VIII
= vestigial sternite VIII. 
Setae:
ads
= anterior dorsal seta; 
as
= anterior seta; 
